Virgin Group Ltd. Founder Richard 
Branson talks about the acquisition of Northern Rock Plc and 
outlook for the company's retail banking operation Virgin Money 
Holdings U.K. Ltd.  He spoke Jan. 9 with Bloomberg's Jeremy Kahn in 
Newscastle, U.K. The story is featured in the May issue of
Bloomberg Markets magazine. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 03:10
 